    <p>
        The information we collect is used to:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Facilitate connections between farmers and energy companies</li>
        <li>Improve our services and user experience</li>
        <li>Send relevant notifications about platform activities</li>
        <li>Provide support and respond to inquiries</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="mt-4">Data Security</h3>
    <p>
        We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access,
        alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic
        storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
    </p>

